      "code": "# search substring in hadith fields\nmatches=[]\nfor rec in h:\n    for field in ['hadithTxt','Matn']:\n        txt = rec.get(field) or ''\n        if not txt: continue\n        if norm_needle in normalize(txt):\n            matches.append((rec['hadithID'], field, txt[:200]))\nlen(matches)",
